Maki & Toji: Party to Pleasure
(NSFW 18+ Parody of Jujutsu Kaisen – In Progress)

Maki arrives at an elegant party hoping to unwind, but the atmosphere leaves her cold: no one pays her any attention, not even the person she was expecting. Dressed to impress, she decides to leave early… until an unexpected encounter with Toji changes everything.

A chance meeting, a glance that lingers too long, and a forbidden chemistry that neither of them can ignore. What begins as a brief conversation ends in a private night where family barriers crumble and desire takes over.
